{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id52f34b53-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3305"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3305"},"text":"§ 3305.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" When transfer is made or obligation is incurred","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"For the purposes of this subchapter:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id52f34b54-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3305/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" A transfer is made—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id52f34b55-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3305/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" with respect to an asset that is real property (other than a fixture, but including the interest of a seller or purchaser under a contract for the sale of the asset), when the transfer is so far perfected that a good-faith purchaser of the asset from the debtor against whom applicable law permits the transfer to be perfected cannot acquire an interest in the asset that is superior to the interest of the transferee; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id52f34b56-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3305/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" with respect to an asset that is not real property or that is a fixture, when the transfer is so far perfected that a creditor on a simple contract cannot acquire, otherwise than under this subchapter, a judicial lien that is superior to the interest of the transferee.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id52f34b57-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3305/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If applicable law permits the transfer to be perfected as approved in paragraph (1) and the transfer is not so perfected before the commencement of an action or proceeding for relief under this subchapter, the transfer is deemed made immediately before the commencement of the action or proceeding.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id52f34b58-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3305/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If applicable law does not permit the transfer to be perfected as provided in paragraph (1), the transfer is made when it becomes effective between the debtor and the transferee.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id52f34b59-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3305/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A transfer is not made until the debtor has acquired rights in the asset transferred.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id52f34b5a-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3305/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" An obligation is incurred—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id52f34b5b-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3305/5/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" if oral, when it becomes effective between the parties; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id52f34b5c-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3305/5/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" if evidenced by a writing executed by the obligor, when such writing is delivered to or for the benefit of the obligee.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id52f34b5d-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/647/tXXXVI/s3611"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–647, title XXXVI, § 3611","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-11-29"},"text":"Nov. 29, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/4962"},"text":"104 Stat. 4962","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id52f34b5e-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id52f34b5f-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDate","id":"id52f34b60-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section effective 180 days after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-11-29"},"text":"Nov. 29, 1990","children":[],"tail":", and applicable with respect to certain actions for debts owed the United States pending in court on that effective date, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/647/s3631"},"text":"section 3631 of Pub. L. 101–647","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t28/s3001"},"text":"section 3001 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
